Webhook branch contains simple http daemon and simple bash script to process webhook requests from github

It is possible to emulate webhook request by:

curl -v \
    -H 'X-GitHub-Delivery: b8723178-f5b2-11ea-80f6-d98974ca096b' \
    -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
    -d '{"repository": {"full_name": "enp/tent"}, "ref": "refs/heads/application"}' \
    -X POST http://127.0.0.1:18202
